Package: catllm
Title: LLM-Powered Text Classification and Category Extraction
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Chris", "Soria", email = "chrissoria@berkeley.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Chris Soria [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Chris Soria <chrissoria@berkeley.edu>
Description: R interface to the 'catllm' Python package for LLM-powered text
    classification, category extraction, and corpus exploration. Wraps the
    Python classify(), extract(), and explore() functions via 'reticulate',
    allowing R users to leverage large language models for qualitative data
    analysis without writing Python code.
